txt.en: Within Agal Dûn, the fortress of horror, Angmarim of the Iron Crown watch over Câr Bronach. Behind its wall, the presence of the Iron Crown is known with banners strewn about. In steps to reclaim Câr Bronach, these banners must be destroyed.
